<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#163a34" />
  <title>武汉健身与颜面RPG：16周身材皮肤升级系统</title>
  <link rel="manifest" href="./manifest.webmanifest" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="./icons/icon-180.png" />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="./icons/icon-192.png" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent" />
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="身材颜面RPG" />
  <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
  <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
<div class="shell">
  <header class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow" style="color:#eab185">CHARLIE · 武汉身材与颜面 RPG</div>
    <h1>16周身材与颜面RPG：减脂、增肌、体能与皮肤升级</h1>
    <p>把减脂、力量、体能和面部皮肤放进同一个长期系统：训练升级、护肤连击、打Boss、开宝箱。休息日同样是任务，不靠惩罚和透支换进度。</p>
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="metric"><b id="heroWeek">第1周</b><span>当前进度</span></div>
      <div class="metric"><b id="heroLevel">Lv.1</b><span>角色等级</span></div>
      <div class="metric"><b id="heroCoins">0 ◈</b><span>虚拟筹码</span></div>
      <div class="metric"><b id="heroWeight">76.0 kg</b><span>当前体重</span></div>
      <div class="metric"><b id="heroStreak">0周</b><span>连续达标</span></div>
      <div class="metric"><b id="heroScore">0 / 12</b><span>本周积分</span></div>
    </div>
  </header>


  <div id="offlinePill" class="offline-pill">当前离线，已保存的内容仍可使用</div>
  <aside id="installBanner" class="install-banner" aria-live="polite">
    <div class="install-banner-row">
      <div><b>把它装到手机桌面</b><p>全屏打开、离线可用，使用体验更接近独立 App。</p></div>
      <div class="install-actions">
        <button id="installApp" class="install-primary" type="button">安装方法</button>
        <button id="dismissInstall" class="install-close" type="button" aria-label="关闭">稍后</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="installHelp" class="install-help">
      <b>iPhone 安装步骤</b>
      <ol><li>务必使用 Safari 打开部署后的网址。</li><li>点击底部“分享”按钮。</li><li>向下滑动并选择“添加到主屏幕”。</li><li>点击右上角“添加”，以后从桌面进入。</li></ol>
      <span class="tiny muted">首次打开需要联网；之后主要页面可以离线使用。数据保存在这台设备的浏览器中，建议定期导出备份。</span>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <nav class="tabs" aria-label="页面导航">
    <button class="tab active" data-tab="today"><span class="nav-icon">⌂</span><span class="nav-label">今天</span></button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="training"><span class="nav-icon">◆</span><span class="nav-label">训练</span></button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="food"><span class="nav-icon">◉</span><span class="nav-label">饮食</span></button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="skin"><span class="nav-icon">✦</span><span class="nav-label">颜面</span></button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="log"><span class="nav-icon">＋</span><span class="nav-label">记录</span></button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="game"><span class="nav-icon">♛</span><span class="nav-label">游戏</span></button>
    <button class="tab" data-tab="settings"><span class="nav-icon">⚙</span><span class="nav-label">设置</span></button>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section id="today" class="panel active">
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card span-8">
          <div class="today-title">
            <div><div class="eyebrow" id="dateLabel"></div><h2 id="todayHeading">今天的任务</h2></div>
            <span class="phase" id="phaseLabel">适应期</span>
          </div>
          <div id="todayTasks"></div>
          <div class="btn-row">
            <button class="btn" id="completeMain">完成今天主训练</button>
            <button class="btn secondary" id="useMinimum">今天改做15分钟保底版</button>
            <button class="btn ghost" onclick="switchTab('training')">查看动作详情</button>
          </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="card span-4">
          <div class="eyebrow">本周完成度</div>
          <div class="score-big"><span id="weekScore">0</span><small> / 12分</small></div>
          <div class="progress"><i id="scoreBar"></i></div>
          <p class="small muted" id="scoreMessage">先完成一次训练，系统就开始运转。</p>
          <div class="notice" style="margin-top:12px"><b>本周成功线：</b>8分。6—7分也算保底成功；不要为了满分破坏恢复。</div>
        </aside>

        <article class="card span-12">
          <div class="today-title"><div><div class="eyebrow">WEEKLY MAP</div><h2>本周安排</h2></div><button class="btn secondary" id="resetWeek">重置本周勾选</button></div>
          <div class="week-grid" id="weekGrid"></div>
        </article>

        <article class="card span-7">
          <div class="eyebrow">今日吃法</div><h2 id="mealTodayTitle">第1天食谱</h2>
          <div id="todayMeals"></div>
          <button class="btn secondary" onclick="switchTab('food')">查看7天完整菜单与替换方案</button>
        </article>

        <aside class="card span-5">
          <div class="eyebrow">今日提示</div>
          <p class="quote" id="dailyQuote">只做今天需要做的，不提前焦虑16周。</p>
          <div id="gameNudge" class="notice" style="margin-bottom:10px"><b>今日奖励：</b>完成主任务后可开启一次随机宝箱。</div>
          <div class="notice warn"><b>隐匿性肾炎底线：</b>不暴汗脱水、不自行高蛋白冲量、不把肌酸/氮泵/燃脂剂作为计划必需品。出现肉眼血尿、明显水肿、尿量异常或血压显著升高时暂停高强度训练。</div>
        </aside>

        <article class="card span-12">
          <div class="today-title"><div><div class="eyebrow">FACE QUEST</div><h2>今日颜面升级任务</h2></div><button class="btn secondary" type="button" onclick="switchTab('skin')">查看完整方案</button></div>
          <div id="skinTodayTasks" class="skin-task-row"></div>
          <p class="small muted" id="skinTodayNote">先把清洁、保湿、防晒和循序渐进的祛痘治疗做稳定，医美排在活动性痤疮控制之后。</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="training" class="panel">
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card span-12">
          <div class="eyebrow">16-WEEK ROADMAP</div><h2>四阶段推进</h2>
          <div class="grid">
            <div class="card span-6 phase-card"><h3>第1—4周｜重新启动</h3><p>第1—2周每周2次力量＋2次轻有氧；第3周开始尝试3次力量；第4周减量并做第一次测试。</p><span class="pill">成功标准：累计8次力量</span></div>
            <div class="card span-6 phase-card"><h3>第5—8周｜减脂与增肌基础</h3><p>稳定3次力量＋1次持续有氧＋1次兴趣运动。日均步数逐步达到7000—8000。</p><span class="pill">第8周减量复测</span></div>
            <div class="card span-6 phase-card"><h3>第9—12周｜体能提高</h3><p>维持力量训练；加入1次低强度间歇。篮球从投篮、移动和低对抗半场开始。</p><span class="pill">仍不做全力冲刺</span></div>
            <div class="card span-6 phase-card"><h3>第13—16周｜形成长期系统</h3><p>不再堆训练量，追求动作、力量、腰围和执行稳定性。第16周减量并完成结业测试。